data.description: Welcome home! This beautifully crafted 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom home, boasting 2,360 square feet, offers USDA eligibility with 0% down to those who qualify. This home is a true gem! Your new home provides a breathtaking view of the serene community pond. Enjoy the tranquility and peaceful surroundings as you take in the sights and sounds of nature from your very own backyard. Residents also have the privilege of access to the community pond, perfect for walks, picnics, or simply unwinding by the water's edge. Beyond your private oasis, the community offers a refreshing pool, a hub of summertime fun and relaxation. Step inside, and you'll be welcomed by an open and inviting floor plan that combines the living, dining, and kitchen areas. The heart of this home is the spacious kitchen, including a large island - perfect for meal preparation and casual dining with abundant counter space and modern appliances. With four generously sized bedrooms, this home offers ample space for your family and guests. The master suite is a haven of comfort, featuring a private bathroom with separate tub and shower, and a huge walk in closet for your convenience. The additional bedrooms are versatile and can easily adapt to your family's needs. At an attractive price of $350,000, this home represents an excellent opportunity to become part of a wonderful community. Don't miss out on the chance to make this house your forever home. Contact us today to schedule a viewing and experience the beauty and convenience for yourself.
